{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778547107197,"sessionID":"ses_1e66dfeceffeFJTRMEaU0l391Y","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-b5455ca169bd0fe1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary of Changes\n- Removed `UBERON:0002835` (thoracic dorsal root ganglion) as a subclass of `UBERON:0000961` (thoracic ganglion).\n- Renamed `UBERON:0000961` from \"thoracic ganglion\" to \"thoracic paravertebral ganglion\".\n\n## Rationale\nDorsal root ganglia are not paravertebral/sympathetic ganglia. The thoracic ganglion (UBERON:0000961) is defined as a paravertebral ganglion, so the thoracic dorsal root ganglion should not be its subclass. \n\nRenaming \"thoracic ganglion\" to \"thoracic paravertebral ganglion\" clarifies that it refers specifically to the sympathetic paravertebral ganglia of the thorax, rather than any ganglion located within the thoracic region.\n\n## Validation\n- Verified the IDs of the affected terms using `obo-grep.pl`.\n- Verified the current definitions and relationships in `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n- Performed the edits using `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl`.\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778547107192,"end":1778547107196}},"id":"prt_e19ab1160001zWOYodHkRYVA2L","sessionID":"ses_1e66dfeceffeFJTRMEaU0l391Y","messageID":"msg_e19ab0f0e001ixq20JQYFllzaC"}}
